Package: CausalKnowledgeTrace
Type: Project
Title: Causal Knowledge Trace - Interactive DAG Analysis Application
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-01-08
Authors@R: c(
    person("CausalKnowledgeTrace", "Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "team@causalknowledgetrace.org")
)
Description: An interactive Shiny application for causal directed acyclic graph (DAG) 
    analysis and visualization. Provides tools for loading, analyzing, and visualizing 
    causal relationships with support for DAGitty integration, network statistics, 
    and causal inference analysis including minimal sufficient adjustment sets.
License: MIT
URL: https://github.com/causalknowledgetrace/CausalKnowledgeTrace
BugReports: https://github.com/causalknowledgetrace/CausalKnowledgeTrace/issues
